Package Compiler.ContextualAnalysis

Class TypeCheckerVisitor

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
Compiler.AntlrGenerated.BuffBaseVisitor<java.lang.Integer>
Compiler.ContextualAnalysis.TypeCheckerVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
BuffVisitor<java.lang.Integer>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<java.lang.Integer>
public class TypeCheckerVisitor
extends BuffBaseVisitor<java.lang.Integer>
The type checker validates the type for: - return statement/return type correspondence in function definition - if-statement conditions (should be of type bool) - expression operations - function call parameters/function definition type correspondence
